{"tid":1861683,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中共企圖謀殺港人 危害香港已經明目張膽","createTime":"2020-02-04T08:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T14:46:11.000Z","uid":11919,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c25adba62175c0df82a75b27502605ea4c114f26","tid":1861683,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:41:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一國兩制下 中共管治誠信破產 </span><br />\n持續至今既反送中運動 <br />\n下令黑警在港濫捕濫權 行使暴力 對香港人既抹黑 以黑社會去製造人民鬥爭既假象 <br />\n<br />\n防疫無能 隱藏疫情<br />\n中國肺炎危害港人 中共政府無所作為 下令部分城市封城 但忽略香港 人封關訴求 企圖報復香港人(澳門已封關) <br />\n<br />\n係中共政權既管治下 香港必定收皮<br />\n講左咁多野 只有一句口號可以解決危機<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立 唯一出路</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d4a94202c11d4806ece490a0ceec7ea3fb2fa132","tid":1861683,"uid":260817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:41:52.000Z","msg":"推上熱門：美孚人，今晚7點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1861651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1861651</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4338037e4da310a8ce4bab0b043ef4e41fcd2f5b","tid":1861683,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38078eb334d9d993ff16d9bfb2e69e151c3e854e","tid":1861683,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"殺緊啦 仲企圖"},{"pid":"aabaee78e906c365498f159da8277aa6514b9c8c","tid":1861683,"uid":230911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38078eb334d9d993ff16d9bfb2e69e151c3e854e","tid":1861683,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"殺緊啦 仲企圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無錯"},{"pid":"042a1dac40b9985b8d7ce75960d01cc077a71978","tid":1861683,"uid":111406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:59:01.000Z","msg":